examples.en: A good driver has quick reactions.
The speed of his reactions saved his life.
A lot of chemical reactions are reversible.
He was puzzled by the reactions to his remark.
examples.ru: Он был озадачен реакцией на своё замечание.

examples.en: The chemists schematized the various reactions in a coherent fashion.
The government is clearly testing the water, to gauge the country's reactions to their proposals.
examples.ru: Правительство явно проверяет почву, чтобы оценить реакцию населения страны на свои предложения.
